Interface VariableReference

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, Expression, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    VariableReferenceImpl

    public interface VariableReference
extends Expression
    A representation of the model object 'Variable Reference'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Aggregator
    • Var
    • Variable

      • getVar

        java.lang.String getVar()
        Returns the value of the 'Var' attribute.

        Warning! This feature contains the original reference text, not the variable name. For variable name, use the #variable/Variable.getName() reference chain. This is significant when using anonymous variables (named '_').
